{"tid":2421160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德福和你Shop衝突10名青年被控非法集結","createTime":"2021-02-24T10:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T12:16:58.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8361af574daff8dd5fcdfa1b95c82a864782d243","tid":2421160,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:24:16.000Z","msg":"前年12月網民連日號召到商場「和你Shop」，引發衝突，多人被捕。同月28日在九龍灣德福廣場被捕的10名青年，被控非法集結等罪，案件今於觀塘裁判法院開審，其中7人未成年。控方證人作供期間，提及自己從網上找到有關活動的資料，控方加以追問詳情；辯方聞言群起反對，指控方事前沒有披露相關資料，對被告造成不公。惟最終裁判官<span class=\"red\">屈麗雯</span>批准繼續提問，指可作為案件的背景資料。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">德福廣場保安經理朱家培</span>今出庭作供稱自己從<span class=\"red\">連登</span>網站和Telegram帖文中，得知當日商場有遊行活動。<br />\n<br />\n另外案件開審前，控方一度指由於沒有片段拍攝到次被告楊**參與非法集結，<span class=\"red\">提出以被告承認的襲警罪內容，證明他有共同目的參與非法集結</span>。辯方反對，指若以襲警作為共同目的，則所有被告理應即時罪名不成立。控方澄清指相關指控只針對第二被告。審訊明續。"},{"pid":"3e598c6704b1e4b57afa5e9f6200a32057429d72","tid":2421160,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210224/7EZVAXGJKVGADEIITTTITAC5KA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210224%2F7EZVAXGJKVGADEIITTTITAC5KA%2F&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8GAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=04ceb394\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210224%2F7EZVAXGJKVGADEIITTTITAC5KA%2F&h=2dbb8a81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210224/7EZVAXGJKVGADEIITTTITAC5KA/</a>"},{"pid":"870ae97d3451ff2d050945d3f0346864793a8bd8","tid":2421160,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58314e7106e3243c804809397c563d90e9198ea1","tid":2421160,"uid":128328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">德福廣場保安經理朱家培</span>"},{"pid":"8c5f91012e18e4ae78813aad0520980ff1fc68af","tid":2421160,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea6c29554e1115628dca8cc5ad86db1b9658673","tid":2421160,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cfbf37348845801a040e33bbbf0e55e9461181","tid":2421160,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:36:40.000Z","msg":"有冇人識朱生"},{"pid":"a06064d039ec6871be164349d85366528afab338","tid":2421160,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a364859993f7b4e28415500f5c1b26870c3e8b6","tid":2421160,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d6e62ac35e36676d5fadec116090be923a8f4a","tid":2421160,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}